                             'MYTiles' 1.03

                           by Charles-N. Jacob

  @{" MyTiles " link play} is a game where you try to clear all the game boards
that are filled with numbered tiles. All you have to do is to find
a numbered tile that matches the 'Next tile', located on the right
in the window. Once the tile is found, a new tile is displayed and
so on, until the entire game board is cleared.

  Have fun!

